high_descs: Go straight and to the right to the oven.
Take the pot from the back left burner on the stove top.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the pot in the refrigerator's right side next to the lettuce. Close then open the refrigerator.
Turn left and go to the oven.
Put the pot on the back left burner on the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the stove top.

high_descs: walk over to the kitchen stove
grab the pot off of the back left burner on the stove
walk on over to the fridge
put the pot in the fridge to cool then take it back out again
head back over to the kitchen stove
place the pot back on the same burner you first picked it up from
anns.task_desc: cool a pot that was on the stove

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, turn to face the stove on the left.
Pick up the pot on the left side of the stove
turn around and walk forward, face the refrigerator on the left
Open the refrigerator and put the pot inside and close it. Open it back up and remove the pot
Turn left and walk forward to the stove and face the stove
Put the pot back on the left burner of the stove
anns.task_desc: put a pot in the refrigerator and on to the stove
